snippet.title: Box Office - X-Men Apocalypse vs Rotten Tomatoes, Alice Through the Looking Glass vs Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Box Office analysis today for X-Men Apocalypse, Alice Through the Looking Glass, The Angry Birds Movie and Disney movies breakdown!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

In this box office recap find out how both X-Men Apocalypse and Alice Through the Looking Glass fell short Memorial Day weekend, May 27th 2016!  Are Rotten Tomatoes and Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp to blame?! Also a breakdown of Disney in 2016 including mega hits Captain America Civil War, Zootopia and The Jungle Book!  Plus find out what the industry is projecting for Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2, Me Before You and Popstar!  Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph gives you an inside look at the weekend box office with an industry perspective!  Be sure to make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for movie and entertainment news here on YouTube today!

CHAPTER TIMES
Intro - 00:00
X-Men Apocalypse - 1:01
Alice Through the Looking Glass - 4:21
Disney 2016 Box Office - 8:11
Sony Animation & Angry Birds - 10:24

The Nice Guys - 13:31
Other Movies - 14:33
